Full image archive: [url=http://titan614.com/images/]Index of /images[/url]
[b]Features[/b]
[ul][li]Stealing from stalls in Ardy work[/li] [li]Potion refilling (using potions (1) on potions (20 etc.)[/li] [li]Able to clean all herbs which are thievable or buyable[/li] [li]Duel arena fully added![/li] [li]Wrath prayer added[/li] [li]Command system rewritten for stability and efficiency[/li] [li]Fully re-arrangeable spell books (moderns, ancients, lunars)[/li] [li]Achievment tab contains useful game information about your account[/li] [li]Unique Tournament System[/li] [li]Fully working woodcutting system, all trees work[/li] [li]Morrigans throwing axe and javelins[/li] [li]All correct projectiles for ranged weapons[/li] [li]Ancients autocasting[/li] [li]Dicing arena for those who love gambling their money[/li] [li]Private message colouring[/li] [li]Voting for rewards[/li] [li]Working Clan Chats![/li][/ul]
